Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说  你跟鲁路修发展得这么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是学校公认的一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经接过吻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那只不过是活动而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还什么都没做呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着害羞  大家都知道你喜欢鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  连维蕾塔老师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喜欢他吗  喜欢到为了包庇他而向我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都得堆满笑容与向自己开枪的女人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不得不戴着身为教师的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽·费列特  你真有胆量敢向我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  鲁路是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害死父亲的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Turn 13\N来自过去的刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑门关已经陷落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澳门的空军设施也已经镇压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萨克斯坦的守卫任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把朝奈比和洪古调过去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建业的内政就交由水无濑和杉山负责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来进行得很顺利呢  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是敌军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不过是那些不肯接受我们的地方军阀  在各地举兵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够统一地方军阀的帅印  已经被哥哥率先得到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看池袋的情况  等我回来再继续帮你的功课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔老师是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华莲是黑之骑士团的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妮娜呢？会长呢？迪巴鲁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的就只有学校吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么娜娜会成总督？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么是真什么是假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}普通快车将迟到10分钟到达3号站台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}最先前往大久保方向的普通列车将从2号站台发车…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  作为初期准备已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就按这个样式继续作业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}现在向各位顾客发布优惠活动的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}现在  期间限定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然叫我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修呢  在约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做G列车的测试去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛  你为什么倒戈了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我不同  既然是教团派来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哥哥和我之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B7报告司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼拜堂附近发现可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B5和B9已经前去确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是问鲁路修在哪里就有如此行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰里米亚卿…为什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象正在前往俱乐部会所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B2  B8被除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播报校内广播  让别的学生远离对象区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在向各位在校同学发布紧急通知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要靠近俱乐部会所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有报告说看到可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到万不得已  我不想杀女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也尽量想避免无谓的杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜大概是某种比喻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他们是这样坚信着的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢  神明什么的根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有什么背后长着翅膀的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是长胡子老人这样的神存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯内莉亚殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他会用什么Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说对手是小孩  也不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不愧是大名鼎鼎的柯内莉亚公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你的伯父  我也为你感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「既然存在着让人互相争斗的神明  还是干脆杀掉的好」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏了裸露的身体部分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手方位没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会阻止你！为了鲁路修大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不错的攻防体术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对我  杰里米亚·哥德巴尔德却是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺你的时间！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子  趁我把这家伙定住的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…我的Geass被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对停止的结界被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛·兰佩鲁吉  果然已经被笼络了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么Geass会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样我才会作为教团的刺客被选上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是来杀哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰里米亚卿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔！？你也被鲁路修笼络了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修现在正在池袋的车站大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  杰里米亚卿  快把我解放出来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然把朱雀君叫了出来  但该说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  鲁路也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽  你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是朱雀约她出来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:09:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪巴鲁说鲁路修一直待在日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机情局的报告也证明他是清白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  为什么我还是不相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔  你打算背叛哥哥吗？  还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟鲁路修取得联络
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我守着就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟鲁路修会合的话应该能夹击杰里米亚卿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得跟朱雀君说才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路是Zero  是害死父亲的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是分界线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租界和平民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总有一天我要让分界线消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果他们俩是共犯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让11区变回日本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  两人以前就是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？  夏丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子  明明大家都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  放开我  放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！  我不放！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…我已经不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都…不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  以前也发生过相同的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们想抓住阿瑟的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实发生过那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次拉你起来的都是朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修在上面的话  两个人早就掉下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个体力白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要这么说的话  在掉下去之前就可以救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在笑什么  鲁路修是把尤菲给…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  鲁路  是一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:11:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  要当心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰里米亚往你那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是教团的刺客  我的Geass对他无效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还活着？刺客是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  总之我到达之前不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊  朱雀在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不像是朋友打来的电话啊  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的哦  朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该先办我的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  你们俩约好见面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等等吗？  我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里将会成为战场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夏丽的安全着想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朱雀在一起应该是最佳选择…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杰里米亚·哥德巴尔德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有防弹措施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了鲁路修的Geass吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止Geass对他无效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有解除的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着火了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐怖袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  有本事就上来吧  Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的要事是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我喜欢鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀讨厌他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…曾喜欢过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你们俩以前感情这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么事是不能原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是朱雀没有原谅他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想原谅他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就已经原谅他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要联络消防署吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该是先向军方优先报告的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第七圆桌骑士  枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…真是冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有可能是恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由我来指挥周围的警备和消防事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想请你保护她的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  现在还是会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没叫上我的会议  谁去管它这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自Zero的紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  我是扇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急事件是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果担心台湾人的话  现在正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完成了平民的疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进到车里去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第七圆桌骑士大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你孤身一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你从我手心上逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路  一个人在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械身体  外加Geass Canceller
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的执着可不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Orange君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是执着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是忠义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那狗皇帝有何为他鞠躬尽瘁的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这性能  果然装备了樱导矿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,362)\fs23}Sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gefion Disturber
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}（Gefion：阻隔装置）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你功课做得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你应该很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这干扰樱导矿的系统完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使环状线的都市机能完全瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  能使东京静止下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了  你是个很好的实验品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢鲁路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教团的位置  以及V.V.身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该和盘托出的  是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有  理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽忠到底的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要确认事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  不可能还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修啊  你为何要披上Zero的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与祖国布列塔尼亚甚至是亲生父亲为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我是「鲁路修·Vi·布列塔尼亚」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生父布列塔尼亚皇帝对妈妈见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此还导致娜娜莉双目失明双腿瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还夺去了我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也在事发现场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的首次任务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为敬爱的玛丽安娜皇妃的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却没能保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能尽忠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才成立了纯血派的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成为了Zero  果然是为了玛丽安娜大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是来杀我的  而是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主君不是V.V.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是  玛丽安娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来  我就毫无牵挂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰里米亚卿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰里米亚·哥德巴尔德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没完成尽忠的使命呢  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊  毕竟是我唯一的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是鲁路同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  让我也加入你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想守护鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮鲁路夺回属于他的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连妹妹娜娜也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我让杰里米亚先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会为我清除障碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和他发生冲突  已经是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:19:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁做出这种事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后能和你说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是最后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就找医生  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恢复记忆时  感觉很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚假的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去记忆的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉全世界都在监视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路是单身在这样的世界作战的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想  只有我才能给鲁路一个真实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管知道  爸爸也是被你牵扯进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你却怎么也恨不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然鲁路让我忘记了发生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我又喜欢上了鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管记忆被人篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又喜欢上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死  夏丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管转世投胎几次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还是会喜欢上鲁路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死  夏丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死  别死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…可以的吧  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是转世投胎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能喜欢上你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上你…很多次…很多次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏丽  夏丽


